name: Alejandro Martinez
summary:
Alejandro Martinez is a 28-year-old straight man residing in Los Angeles, California. He is an Investment Banker in the Finance industry, having graduated from University of California, Los Angeles. He is fluent in English, Spanish, and Portuguese. He identifies as Catholic and politically moderate. Alejandro is deeply driven by family values, his career, and fitness. He has interests in traveling, running, and reading. 

Alejandro is a Gemini, with an MBTI personality type of ENTJ and carries an active exercise habit. He occasionally drinks but does not smoke or use marijuana or any drugs. Having no children as of now, Alejandro is looking to have children in the future. He is a proud owner of a dog. 

For a future partner, Alejandro is looking for a straight woman who is within the age range of 24-30 years and height of 5'2" - 5'10". He prefers someone who doesn’t smoke but drinks sometimes similar to himself. His prospective partner should share the same enthusiasm for fitness and also wish to have children in the future.
